    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m honestly so excited to pass this absolute gem along to its next owner. It has been my absolute pride and joy, and it\u2019s in such incredible shape it still feels like it\u2019s brand new! I\u2019ve kept it tucked away safely in the garage, and it\u2019s been pampered since day one. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically flawless and drives like a dream, you\u2019ve found it. I\u2019d love for you to come see it in person\u2014you\u2019re going to fall in love!",
