      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my absolute pride and joy, and let me tell you, she is a total beauty! This car is in absolutely pristine condition\u2014it honestly looks and feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve babied this ride since day one, keeping it garage-stored and sparkling clean. If you\u2019re looking for a dream car that\u2019s been cared for with a lot of love, you\u2019ve found it! I'm so excited for the next owner to enjoy it as much as I have. Feel free to reach out with any questions!",
